<item>
            <title>[FLINK-3933] Add an auto-type-extracting DeserializationSchema</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-3933</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When creating a &lt;tt&gt;DeserializationSchema&lt;/tt&gt;, people need to manually worry about how to provide the produced type&apos;s &lt;tt&gt;TypeInformation&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should add a base utility &lt;tt&gt;AbstractDeserializationSchema&lt;/tt&gt; that provides that automatically via the type extractor.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12971106">FLINK-3933</key>
